(95, 'Alice', 'Unable to meet in the city, Alice and Alex embark on an emotional journey of love and loss.', 404031, '0.0', 0, '/83hP8JXrZY5Hf6IBkG8USFzf3K2.jpg', '2005-08-30', NULL, '[]', NULL),
(96, 'Alice', 'The story of a young couple who are expecting their first baby. We see Amanda’s anxiety and trepidation at the impending change in her life, and what it will mean to her. After tragedy strikes, we see the couple\'s crushed hopes and grief at their loss, and how they eventually move towards an acceptance of what has happened in their lives, and of each other.', 507594, '0.0', 0, '/yb47XfDJJF6uNFEEi8rItnMSuJz.jpg', '2003-02-26', NULL, '[18]', NULL),
(97, 'Alice', 'Seven years after the abduction of his daughter Alice, Jacques leads a life suspended in waiting.  The days pass by, between the routine of his work as a storekeeper and the emptiness of the family home.  As a usual day ends, strange details disturb Jacques\' daily life and gradually awaken his existence ...', 659742, '6.7', 9, NULL, '2019-09-14', NULL, '[14]', NULL),
(98, 'Alice', 'Shot in New York in the mid-1970s, Maria Lassnig\'s Alice is an unconventional portrait of the titular woman, with footage of her body accented by superimposed fireworks, Händel, and Lassnig\'s laconic voice-over.', 544400, '0.0', 0, '/fozkTh3PQsHswnNFL03mVg9xU2u.jpg', '2018-01-29', NULL, '[18]', NULL),
(99, 'Alice', 'Locked in an austere country house, headstrong and spirited Alice yearns for the freedom of the forest. But as Alice discovers the power of seduction, it is more than just her desire that is awakened…\r Adapted for the screen by Laura Scrivano. Based on Noel Coward\'s Alice Is At It Again.', 702009, '8.0', 1, '/4f9C2SANPrH0ckQabrLoAuDmYgC.jpg', '2017-07-01', NULL, '[18]', NULL),
(100, 'Alice', 'In 1967, when 10 year old Mary refuses to go to school, she is arbitrary sent to a psychiatric hospital where mysticism is her only escape from the maltreatment.', 303415, '7.5', 2, NULL, '2013-10-01', NULL, '[]', NULL),
(101, 'Cyber Hell : Le réseau de l\'horreur', 'Synonyme d\'anonymat et d\'exploitation, un réseau d\'espaces de chat est le théâtre de nombreux crimes sexuels. La traque de ses opérateurs nécessitera courage et ténacité.', 965143, '7.2', 90, '/Ao9mpFYbarCyJogmVvKF2fmXGIi.jpg', '2022-05-17', NULL, '[99]', '/okUGREWC4LN2TSjFX0AOiNJhzdN.jpg'),
(102, 'Rassemblement : le making-of de Deadpool & Wolverine', 'On a imploré Hugh Jackman et Ryan Reynolds, et le réalisateur Shawn Levy (et plein d\'autres, dont t\'as jamais entendu parler, mais tous choupis néanmoins), de nous balancer leurs vérités sur la conception, la gestation et l\'accouchement de Deadpool & Wolverine. En vrai, ils ont l\'obligation contractuelle de divulguer toutes ces infos, mais ils arrivent quand même à donner l\'impression qu\'ils avaient vraiment envie de le faire, limite c\'est eux qui ont eu l\'idée. Allez, fais-toi plaisir !', 1386628, '6.5', 14, '/3dQyDFxTY6o3v67ncYCExog6aPH.jpg', '2024-11-12', NULL, '[99]', '/7cJUnAvP8ntF9KKYm4v8674n0et.jpg'),
